The paper deals with a downlink precoding scheme in a multi-cell massive MIMO system, which involves power control, interference management, antenna switching, and user throughput. These are all related to information theory (cs.IT), networking (cs.NI), control systems (cs.SY), machine learning (cs.MM), and learning (cs.LG). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
